display_name: SourcingScenario transformation - 1000 - RAW test data sets_31 - Ariba Sourcing - 3

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
'SourcingScenario_' || "SourcingScenario"."AlternativeId" as "ID",
'RFXDocument_' || "SourcingScenario"."ContentDocumentReference_documentId" as "RFXDocument",
"SourcingScenario"."AlternativeId" as "AlternativeId",
"SourcingScenario"."AwardStatus" as "AwardStatus",
"SourcingScenario"."AlternativeStatus" as "AlternativeStatus",
"SourcingScenario"."SliceType" as "SliceType",
"SourcingScenario"."ObjectiveFunction" as "ObjectiveFunction",
TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingScenario"."SavedDate") AS "SavedDate",
"SourcingScenario"."Title" as "Title",
"SourcingScenario"."SliceId" as "SliceId",
"SourcingScenario"."IsEmailBid" as "IsEmailBid",
TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingScenario"."SubmissionDate") AS "SubmissionDate",
TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingScenario"."TimeUpdated") as "TimeUpdated",
"SourcingScenario"."NumberofSelectedItems" as "NumberOfSelectedItems",
TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,"SourcingScenario"."ProcessedDate") AS "ProcessedDate",
TIMESTAMPADD(HOUR,<%=TimezoneOffset%>,cast("SourcingScenario"."TimeCreated" as timestamp)) as "TimeCreated",
"SourcingScenario"."Active" as "Active",
"SourcingScenario"."NumberOfSelectedSuppliers" as "NumberOfSelectedSuppliers",
"SourcingScenario"."ScenarioStatus" as "ScenarioStatus",
"SourcingScenario"."AlternativeType" as "AlternativeType",
"SourcingScenario"."ScenarioType" as "ScenarioType",
"SourcingScenario"."Title_DefaultStringTranslation" as "TitleDefaultStringTranslation",
"SourcingScenario"."ContentDocumentReference_UniqueName" as "ContectDocumentReferenceUniqueName",
"SourcingScenario"."ContentDocumentReference_documentMinorVersion" as "ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentMinorVersion",
"SourcingScenario"."ContentDocumentReference_documentVersion" as "ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentVersion",
"SourcingScenario"."ContentDocumentReference_documentId" as "ContectDocumentReferenceDocumentId"
FROM "Scenario" as "SourcingScenario"
WHERE 1=1
    AND "SourcingScenario"."Active" = 'true'
